<p class="ql-align-center">编辑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>「天府耍都」</strong>：家庭娱乐中心、魔法学院密室逃脱、11家主题商铺，卡通风格中国风情小镇，超级适合打卡！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">搜图</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200916/28e0e34a92304597b648d9ce34bd061f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">编辑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">搜图</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200916/64498d9e7e3c4387b44f8205769e2f08.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">编辑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>成都首家阿狸授权店-阿狸的茶与店</strong>，一秒穿越童话世界，果茶、酸奶等主题饮品肉测相当爽口，逛游乐园的绝佳cp！还有造型Q萌的手伴盲盒等，软到心坎坎。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">搜图</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200916/72ff2f5d5f644fba82a0cc62b775e8d9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">编辑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>「蜀汉风云」</strong>：海盗船、空中漫舞、魔力转圈圈、草船借箭等。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">搜图</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200916/72e52ba191d94fc4afb6d332f8a7d432.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">编辑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>「藏羌秘境」</strong>：藏羌探险、秘境漂流、秘境大摆锤。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">搜图</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200916/83099bb32f554b21ac366fce0a99df9d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">编辑</p>
<p><strong>「星际传奇」</strong>：遨游天际、星际俱乐部、弹跳火箭、飞船基地。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong></strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>搜图</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>编辑</strong></p>
